@speaker2: "...that's one learning affecting learning is one way ai is acting as a leverage. the other maybe more intuitive one is this ai agent...this is probably the most interesting research area in 2025 and many more...here ai agent is combining the two types of leverage mechanisms that we saw before...the first one's the human labor because ai agent is doing the work for you...and then the second part is at least the current ai agents are you know software only...you can copy and paste...if you want 10 output 10 agents working together, just do it. if you want 12, just copy two more and you don't have to ask for the permission, this permission-less form of composite leverage mechanism that i think is quite profound...i think that's going to be main source of wealth generation going forward and this thing is very new, i think it's just got started..."
